{"tid":1736914,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【仲未夠】有伊利沙伯醫院醫護即日起罷工抗議","createTime":"2019-11-18T22:47:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T17:11:19.000Z","uid":202464,"like":1059,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":143,"replies":[{"pid":"83362232b7f79460fae3d450ad75f6e567dfcc7a","tid":1736914,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T22:47:34.000Z","msg":"1. 醫護人員指，有醫院同僚向醫院內的警員話：「你哋唔好放（催淚彈）啦」，<br />\n<br />\n該警員回應：「屌你老母」，令當事人非常憤怒。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. 伊院周二可能因被警方催淚彈問題，出現一定規模罷工，各部門都有人參與，某些部門更可能癱瘓。<br />\n<br />\n3. 由周一晚上10時起至周二晚，伊院急症室將不接收緊急及以下級別病人<br />\n<br />\n4. 樽裝醫療氣數量有限，萬一用完未能填補，會影響緊急手術，所以取消部份預約手術<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1bc61e1aaa9de29faa08affb812bc263afddbbc","tid":1736914,"uid":326463,"like":112,"dislike":0,"score":112,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T22:49:35.000Z","msg":"良心醫護"},{"pid":"4c72c6ad3428608e0aef0e8eb183dea28c37c466","tid":1736914,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T22:50:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1335451819191a418801b9168501b5b606a53ea","tid":1736914,"uid":133319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T22:50:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a87493c25b66ac31d3cc5e571ab5df194f314801","tid":1736914,"uid":202464,"like":118,"dislike":3,"score":115,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T22:51:32.000Z","msg":"仲未夠。太保守了。"},{"pid":"3f7554a02d2ddb348796912dd7cee834f83cfd2c","tid":1736914,"uid":105872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T22:53:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b4aa6828b3f94f7764d93142c18574d54302a656","tid":1736914,"uid":279616,"like":172,"dislike":0,"score":172,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T22:54:19.000Z","msg":"正面抗爭以外，生活上全方位杯葛所有<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">狗連家屬</span></span>"},{"pid":"24898e